OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F396A1778058353
OL,3,CSupporter arrested following reports
OL,4,Cplayer racially abused
OL,6,FManchester City have condemned racist
OL,7,Fabuse that was directed towards
OL,8,FAntoine Semenyo during their 3-3 draw
OL,9,Fat Everton's Hill Dickinson stadium on
OL,10,FMonday evening.
OL,12,FSemenyo was the victim of abuse during
OL,13,Fthe match at the stadium, while abuse
OL,14,Fwas directed towards Guehi on social
OL,15,Fmedia after the match in which City
OL,16,Fdropped key points in the title race
OL,17,Fagainst Arsenal.
OL,1,W~k4j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G1/6
