CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F396A1778058353
OL,3,CSupporter arrested following reports
OL,4,Cplayer racially abused
OL,6,FA statement from City said:
OL,7,F"Manchester City strongly condemns the
OL,8,Fracist abuse directed towards Antoine
OL,9,FSemenyo at yesterday's match.
OL,11,F"We welcome the swift action taken by
OL,12,FEverton and the police to identify the
OL,13,Findividual responsible.
OL,15,F"We are also incredibly disappointed
OL,16,Fto hear that Marc Guehi was subject to
OL,17,Fa series of vile racist social media
OL,18,Fposts last night.
OL,26,@oD@AOUsD@AOUwD@AOU
OL,1,W~k4j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G2/6
OL,2,W/*%+.-' "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNW Eng NewsCThis Day FReg TV
FL,397,390,120,260,000,100
PN,39603
SC,0003
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F396A1778058353
OL,3,CSupporter arrested following reports
OL,4,Cplayer racially abused
OL,6,F"We will continue to offer our full
OL,7,Fsupport to both Antoine and Marc and
OL,8,Fnever accept discrimination of any
OL,9,Fkind in our game."
OL,11,FA separate statement from Everton said
OL,12,FMerseyside Police had arrested a 71-
OL,13,Fyear-old on suspicion of a racially
OL,14,Faggravated public order offence after
OL,15,Fsupporters and stewards reported the
OL,16,Fincident.
OL,26,@nD@AOUqD@RO]
OL,1,W~k4j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G3/6
OL,2,W/*%+.-' "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,
