PN,39604
SC,0004
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F396A1778058353
OL,3,CSupporter arrested following reports
OL,4,Cplayer racially abused
OL,6,FThe statement said: "He has since been
OL,7,Fbailed with conditions, including
OL,8,Frestrictions preventing him from going
OL,9,Fwithin one mile of any designated
OL,10,Fsports stadium for a period of up to
OL,11,Ffour hours before kick-off, during
OL,12,Fmatches and up to four hours after the
OL,13,Ffinal whistle.
OL,15,F"Racism and discrimination in all
OL,16,Fforms are completely unacceptable.
OL,17,FThey have no place in our stadia, our
OL,18,Fsport or in society, and behaviour of
OL,19,Fthis nature will not be tolerated.
OL,26,@nD@UOUwD@AOU
OL,1,W~k4j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G4/6
OL,2,W/*%+.-' "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNW Eng NewsCThis Day FReg TV
FL,397,390,120,260,000,100
PN,39605
SC,0005
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F396A1778058353
OL,3,CSupporter arrested following reports
OL,4,Cplayer racially abused
OL,6,F"A swift response from fellow
OL,7,Fsupporters, stewards and Merseyside
OL,8,FPolice led to the individual being
OL,9,Fidentified and appropriate action
OL,10,Ftaken.
OL,12,F"The club will continue to work
OL,13,Fclosely with the authorities to
OL,14,Fsupport their investigation and will
OL,15,Ftake the strongest possible action in
OL,16,Fline with its zero-tolerance approach."
OL,26,@nD@AOUtD@AOUxD@gO]
OL,1,W~k4j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G5/6
