PN,39606
SC,0006
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F396A1778058353
OL,3,CSupporter arrested following reports
OL,4,Cplayer racially abused
OL,6,FEngland defender Guehi, who made a key
OL,7,Ferror that led to Everton equalising
OL,8,Fin the second half through Thierno
OL,9,FBarry, had posted on Instagram after
OL,10,Fthe match, writing: "I need to do
OL,11,Fbetter, but we keep going and focused
OL,12,Fon the next. Thank you for your
OL,13,Fsupport as always. Thank you Jesus!"
OL,15,FAfter Barry had cancelled out Jeremy
OL,16,FDoku's first-half goal, Everton
OL,17,Fstormed into a 3-1 lead with a Jake
OL,18,FO'Brien header and another Barry
OL,19,Fstrike, but Erling Haaland pulled one
OL,20,Fback before Doku equalised in the
OL,21,Fseventh minute of stoppage time.
OL,26,@rD@UOUuD@dO]
